Class MolImport

java.lang.Object
  chemaxon.marvin.modules.MolImport
All Implemented Interfaces:
MolImportIface, StereoConstants
public class MolImport
extends java.lang.Object
implements MolImportIface, StereoConstants

Imports MDL Molfile, SDfile, RGfile, RDfile, Rxnfile and (ChemAxon) compressed molfile. In the Molfiles documentation, you can find details about import options.

Since:
Marvin 1.3

skipToNext

public boolean skipToNext()
Skips the remaining parts of the current molecule and positions the file pointer to the next one. Use this method if an error occured but you want to continue reading the file.
